{{Quote|When you're hurting for the girl who could have saved you ''if-only'', Santherian tenho-root extract's your poison: gentle, gentle, like the sun breaking clouds at the end of day...|[[Greglik]]|<ref name="Planet of Twilight">''[[Planet of Twilight]]''</ref>}}
'''Santherian tenho-root''' was a plant whose extract was also a potent drug. It was often used by abusers who desired a sense of escapism. When taking the drug, users often described it's effects as similar to that of watching a sunset.

The extract was immensely effective on [[Falleen/Legends|Falleen]], who would experience intense psychotropic attacks after taking it.

